{"tid":1387514,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"玩遊戲也要追星！韓國人氣手遊角色曝光...竟與IZ*ONE成員相似高達99%！","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T22:39:48.000Z","uid":238483,"like":6,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"549acad82f17d7f85ca94b67146699b0882e5789","tid":1387514,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"感覺真的是直接看著本人畫出來的阿~~~<br />\n<br />\n漫撕男、漫撕女不稀奇，現在流行的是從遊戲中走出來的女神！<br />\n全部都漂亮的IZ*ONE成員中，這次換誰成了廣大遊戲玩家心中的女神呢<br />\n出道後，備受日韓粉絲喜愛的韓國人氣女團IZ*ONE，日前宣布即將在2019年8~9月展開日本巡迴演唱會後，為了帶給粉絲精彩的舞台，目前正在積極練習準備中<br />\n事實上，出身自《PRODUCE48》的新生代國民女團IZ*ONE，不但實力備受肯定，成員們各有特色的美貌也時常成為外界關注的焦點。<br />\n而日前就有韓國網友發現，有一款韓國手遊新曝光的角色人物，不論是外型還是名字，都跟IZ*ONE成員金采源幾乎是同一個模子刻出來的。而該網友將手游的人物截圖放上知名論壇「Theqoo」之後，也立刻引起大家的關心與討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20190730/8dcfff130fa84b41b19838bcf38fd0d7.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fq_70%2Cc_zoom%2Cw_640%2Fimages%2F20190730%2F8dcfff130fa84b41b19838bcf38fd0d7.webp&h=e1e53792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從這個名為「loveidol株式會社」的手遊截圖中可以看到，新出的女性角色留了一頭淺棕色、有瀏海的長捲髮，造型與金采源出道以來至今的形象極為相似。<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20190730/6e02ba2a2495456b9fea216bd62c5730.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fq_70%2Cc_zoom%2Cw_640%2Fimages%2F20190730%2F6e02ba2a2495456b9fea216bd62c5730.webp&h=074d3d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再看到網友的第二張截圖，可以發現角色名字叫做「Chaewon」，跟IZ*ONE成員金采源的名字英文寫法完全一模一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20190730/2a7c70d8286e4bbda9e3bc486537a5ec.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fq_70%2Cc_zoom%2Cw_640%2Fimages%2F20190730%2F2a7c70d8286e4bbda9e3bc486537a5ec.webp&h=325e0a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾乎神複製「金采源」造型、神韻和名字的手游角色「Chaewon」，也讓許多網友忍不住問：「這不就是金采源嗎？」「這根本就是照著金采源的樣子去創造的角色吧！」<br />\n更有網友稱讚金采源的美貌就像從漫畫裡走出來一樣，還笑稱要她趕快去向用了自己「肖像權」的遊戲公司收取版權費，或是爭取代言，趁機賺一筆代言費。<br />\n<br />\n但不論網友覺得像還是不像，在小編眼裡看來是真的滿像的說~~更何況名字都大喇喇寫「Chaewon」了~IZ*ONE的公司真的可以考慮去收一下版權費囉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台媒高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf30403e268d223916e2062fc04886df35973ee0","tid":1387514,"uid":213300,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:22:27.000Z","msg":"支持彩元bbg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7746fa9400851a46bf30cfdf9af6637c20eea24e","tid":1387514,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf30403e268d223916e2062fc04886df35973ee0","tid":1387514,"uid":213300,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:22:27.000Z","msg":"支持彩元bbg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"支持牙現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc7b1919b1a833465f910e331a3dcbae55e1edb","tid":1387514,"uid":76115,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"牙降個鼻邊有咁令"},{"pid":"0203b6c680d97734aa942b1691b528b7bce19a85","tid":1387514,"uid":68678,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"好抄唔抄 抄牙降"},{"pid":"e5acd1fa5892ec6b1ff9d8437dd01c25fa17330b","tid":1387514,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:31:5